At Reliant Medical Group (formerly Fallon Clinic), we are dedicated to providing top-quality primary and specialty care that is uniquely in tune with your life. Skilled physicians collaborate with teams of other medical professionals and staff to ensure that your care is coordinated and patient-centered.  From online services, to multiple locations, to after-hours and weekend care, Reliant Medical Group is designed around your needs.

